    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This rune's magic bestows a resilience reminiscent of a hill giant. While wearing or carrying an object that bears this rune, you have <strong>advantage </strong>on saving throws against being <strong>poisoned</strong>, and you have <strong>resistance </strong>against <strong>poison damage</strong>.</p>\n<p>In addition, you can invoke the rune as a bonus action, gaining <strong>resistance </strong>to <strong>bludgeoning</strong>, <strong>piercing</strong>, and <strong>slashing damage</strong> for 1 minute. Once you invoke this rune, you can't do so again until you finish a <strong>short or long rest</strong>.</p>",
